                     <interp inst="t17980110-17-punish90" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980110-17-defend211 t17980110-17-punish90"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. 
